<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/2240667-tom-leland"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1380569756i/2240667._UX100_CR0,21,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/2240667-tom-leland">Tom Leland</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Really only in the sense that the same concept: the present is the only reality, and happiness depends on our ability to be in it -- is presented with<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Really only in the sense that the same concept: the present is the only reality, and happiness depends on our ability to be in it -- is presented with meditation as a great method for achieving that. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
