<span id="freeTextContainer12612594291849043088">On my most recent appointment, my psychiatrist introduced me to the <a href='https://canadianhealthrecoverycentre.ca/the-seven-pillars-of-mindfulness/' rel='nofollow noopener'>Seven Pillars of Mindfulness</a> and encouraged me to integrate mindfulness with my cognitive behavioral therapy and meditation exercises as a way to help me manage my anxiety. It turns out that these aforesaid pillars are what <i>Jon Kabat-Zinn</i> tackled on this book. Can&apos;t wait to find the free time to read this one (and hopefully learn something substantial for my mental health). :D</span>
  <span id="freeText12612594291849043088" style="display:none">On my most recent appointment, my psychiatrist introduced me to the <a href="https://canadianhealthrecoverycentre.ca/the-seven-pillars-of-mindfulness/" rel="nofollow noopener">Seven Pillars of Mindfulness</a> and encouraged me to integrate mindfulness with my cognitive behavioral therapy and meditation exercises as a way to help me manage my anxiety. It turns out that these aforesaid pillars are what <i>Jon Kabat-Zinn</i> tackled on this book. Can't wait to find the free time to read this one (and hopefully learn something substantial for my mental health). :D</span>
  <a data-text-id="12612594291849043088" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

